An Analysis of Climate Sentiment Across the USA

Xander Atalay

10/20/2021

Introduction:

Our group is taking a look at six different regions in the continental United States: Northeast, Midwest … Our goal is to analyze the sentiment surrounding climate change in those regions by using text mining algorithms on news sources in those regions.
